## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="17ab6-102">你可以使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性来启用的单个控件的视图状态，即使禁用页。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="17ab6-102">You can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to enable view state for an individual control even if it is disabled for the page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="17ab6-103">若要关闭页面的视图状态，并将其打开的页上的特定控件，设置<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A>页面和控件的属性`true`，将其设置<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A>属性页面的已禁用，且设置到<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A>的控件属性到已启用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="17ab6-103">To turn off view state for a page and turn it on for a specific control on the page, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A> property of the page and the control to `true`, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A> property of the page to Disabled, and set the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A> property of the control to Enabled.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="17ab6-104"><xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A>页或控件的属性具有效果才<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A>属性设置为`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="17ab6-104">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A> property of a page or a control has an effect only if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A> property is set to `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="17ab6-105">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A>属性设置为`false`，即使将关闭视图状态<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A>属性设置为已启用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="17ab6-105">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.EnableViewState%2A> property is set to `false`, view state will be turned off even if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ViewStateMode%2A> property is set to Enabled.</span></span>  
  
